", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:42:39"}, {"id": "4742869", "title": "Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d rendering of question mark made up of dollar banknotes on blue background.\" data-id=\"1178728033\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gearstd</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?</h2> <p><span>We previously covered </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724982-zim-integrated-double-tailwinds-trigger-robust-near-term-dividend-prospects\">ZIM Integrated Shipping</a><span> (NYSE:</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZIM\" title=\"ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd.\">ZIM</a></span><span>) in October 2024, discussing why we had upgraded the stock to</span><span> a speculative buy for dividend oriented investors, thanks to</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742869-is-zim-integrated-a-buy-after-the-ex-dividend-date", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4742847", "title": "Brookfield Renewable Partners: One Of My Highest Conviction Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA, Arkansas, Beaver Lake Dam, elevated view\" data-id=\"200457452-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wesley Hitt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I have been bullish on Brookfield Renewable Partners L.P. Limited Partnership Units (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BEP#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Brookfield Renewable Partners L.P. Limited Partnership Units\">BEP</a>) since my initial <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4680278-brookfield-renewable-partners-discounted-6-percent-yielder-that-is-subject-to-growth\">thesis</a> back in May, 2024. While BEP has recently struggled in terms of lifting its share price higher, my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742847-brookfield-renewable-partners-one-of-my-highest-conviction-investments", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:15:07"}, {"id": "4742872", "title": "Adobe: Heading Into Q4, Two Key Ingredients Are Missing", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Adobe headquarters in San Jose, California, USA\" data-id=\"1581810849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jp